# 🏠 House Price Predictor

An advanced machine learning project to predict Boston house prices using Linear Regression, Random Forest, and XGBoost.

## 📊 Features
- Advanced EDA with visualizations
- Supports multiple models with evaluation
- Modular source code for easy reuse
- Custom prediction on user input
- Future-ready: Streamlit UI, API endpoints, etc.


## Project Structure:
house-price-predictor/
├── data/
│   └── boston.csv
├── models/
│   └── trained_model.pkl
├── notebooks/
│   └── EDA_and_Modeling.ipynb
├── src/
│   ├── data_loader.py
│   ├── visualizer.py
│   ├── trainer.py
│   ├── predictor.py
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
